8.14 Split
==========

`-split section|chapter|none' if set to *section* (resp. *chapter*)
create one HTML file per (sub)section (resp. chapter) and separate pages
for Top, ToC, Overview, Index, Glossary, About.  Otherwise, create a
monolithic HTML file that contains the whole document.

   #$T2H_SPLIT = 'section'; $T2H_SPLIT = undef;


